{"tid":1745462,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"提議：眾籌去英國告嗰3個鬼頭警司","createTime":"2019-11-22T08:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T04:14:49.000Z","uid":258680,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05601fa699ea8d49b8b067ebe3aa176331596e00","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:32:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1151954081669115&amp;id=299408173590381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1151954081669115%26id%3D299408173590381&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=dc879d0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1151954081669115&amp;id=299408173590381</a><br />\n<br />\n之前讀史片專頁，有講過話去英國找議員禠奪林鄭一家英國國藉，不過好似冇乜人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者呢一個一樣都係冇人理，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但作為和理非，香港都走到呢一步，諗到乜睇到乜就提議下啦&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左林鄭，啲green object 一樣令香港人異常痛恨，但香港暫時未有可能會有獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而律政司又被港共政府把持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，個冚家驊仲要射半年波咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足又全部被告暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁剩下來我們又可以做得啲乜呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要有常識都知，香港係行普通法既地方，所以所有普通法地方既法院所判決既案件，都會成為案例，而讀史片呢個專頁既作者就提到，唔受理林鄭都可以去英國法院告嗰三個冚家祥英籍警司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而下議院係確定過佢地既公民身份，而一旦係普通法既國家建立左酷刑案例，香港法院就要被迫承認的確有不合理警暴既事實，對未來幾千單暴動同非法集結應該好有利。<br />\n<br />\n詳情既法律細節我真係唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n但海外有冇做律師既手足係覺得可行，從而令港共又跪一次玻璃呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令到距離攬炒又再近一步呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在此班門弄斧，拋磚引玉求討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999，多謝你花左分9幾鐘來睇。"},{"pid":"3ad855e775ef31d803dacb22db3c06e8cc0d0fa8","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"只求引起討論，避免太快沉底<br />\n自推1/20"},{"pid":"90ca85ca01a029849dc8bd095c39af2a548c0edd","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:37:05.000Z","msg":"自推2/20"},{"pid":"f0ac9e6d9b4893b677f40e7cf11aa546944eb4e3","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:38:35.000Z","msg":"自推3/20"},{"pid":"fec9a6f0b489277ccf9d95b303611b9a17eed121","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"自推4/20"},{"pid":"d765e54ca81144191ea684c71bf0744ac41a54e5","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:48:34.000Z","msg":"好認真問架，希望晏啲多啲巴絲打睇到啦<br />\n自推5/20"},{"pid":"ccf51f731c9e44084a5ecd3b6d04a5a595820ba1","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"自推6/20"},{"pid":"adbe3f9942abcc8133a466c837a6f716bbc994e9","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:34:16.000Z","msg":"自推7/20"},{"pid":"acf2aca2a5b4cf0898b195b85c0baaea58760c54","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"自推9/20"},{"pid":"8ee8d9a01bad2bc64bfb7a73428a79dd13aec05e","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:23:31.000Z","msg":"自推8/20"},{"pid":"2ea287519087e48af3dba1b15c350f3c128f42b0","tid":1745462,"uid":8049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61e918b95f292be4fd1331a4b60a4e417d8f499","tid":1745462,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:48:39.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n唔知有冇用呢"},{"pid":"102d9f53ccebbff2cd9081bb58ecbeb89f198b4f","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:02:34.000Z","msg":"自推10/20"},{"pid":"237af17e754727dbc8200fb45b65f9db066d0ae1","tid":1745462,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"推11/20"}]}